---
import CrmLayout from "@crmapp/layouts/CrmLayout.astro";
---
<CrmLayout title="CRM | Clientes | Dashboard KPI" section="clients">
  <div id="clients-dashboard-root" class="crm-stack crm-clients-dashboard">
    <section class="crm-card crm-full">
      <h2>Dashboard KPI de promociones</h2>
      <p class="crm-inline-note">
        Vista operativa con datos reales de reservas importadas, tanto en modo global como por promocion concreta.
      </p>
      <form id="clients-kpi-org-form" class="crm-form crm-form-compact">
        <label>Ambito
          <select id="clients-kpi-promotion-select">
            <option value="">Cargando promociones...</option>
          </select>
        </label>
        <label>Filtro por estado
          <select id="clients-kpi-status-filter">
            <option value="">Todos los estados</option>
            <option value="pre_registered">Preinscrito</option>
            <option value="reservation_sent">Reserva enviada</option>
            <option value="reserved">Reservado</option>
            <option value="adhesion_paid">Adhesion pagada</option>
            <option value="contract_signed">Contrato firmado</option>
            <option value="cancelled">Cancelado</option>
            <option value="discarded">Descartado</option>
            <option value="other">Otro</option>
          </select>
        </label>
        <label class="crm-checkbox-label crm-toggle-label">
          <input id="clients-kpi-only-active" type="checkbox" />
          <span>Solo promociones activas</span>
        </label>
        <div class="crm-actions-row">
          <button type="submit" class="crm-button crm-button-soft">Aplicar</button>
          <button id="clients-kpi-select-top" type="button" class="crm-button crm-button-soft">
            Ir a promocion top
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>
      <p id="clients-kpi-org-meta" class="crm-inline-note"></p>
      <p id="clients-kpi-promo-meta" class="crm-inline-note"></p>
      <div class="crm-dashboard-toolbar">
        <div class="crm-dashboard-toolbar-copy">
          <strong>Vista personalizable</strong>
          <p>
            Activa el modo edicion para mostrar solo lo que necesitas, reordenar bloques y guardar tu vista automaticamente.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="crm-dashboard-toolbar-actions">
          <button
            id="clients-kpi-customize-toggle"
            type="button"
            class="crm-button crm-button-primary"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="clients-kpi-layout-panel"
          >
            Personalizar vista
          </button>
          <button id="clients-kpi-customize-reset" type="button" class="crm-button crm-button-soft">
            Restaurar vista
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <section id="clients-kpi-layout-panel" class="crm-layout-panel" hidden>
        <div class="crm-layout-panel-head">
          <div>
            <h3>Editar dashboard</h3>
            <p class="crm-inline-note">
              Cambia tu vista sin tocar codigo. Los cambios se guardan solos para tu usuario dentro de esta organizacion.
            </p>
          </div>
          <button id="clients-kpi-customize-close" type="button" class="crm-button crm-button-soft">
            Cerrar editor
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="crm-layout-presets">
          <div>
            <strong>Vistas rapidas</strong>
            <p class="crm-inline-note">Empieza por un modelo base y luego ajusta detalle a detalle.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="crm-layout-presets-actions">
            <button type="button" class="crm-layout-preset-button" data-layout-preset="full">
              Vista completa
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="crm-layout-preset-button" data-layout-preset="executive">
              Vista ejecutiva
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="crm-layout-preset-button" data-layout-preset="commercial">
              Seguimiento comercial
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="crm-layout-guide">
          <div class="crm-layout-tip">
            <strong>1. Mostrar u ocultar</strong>
            <p>Usa los botones Mostrar u Ocultar en cada fila para decidir que entra en tu vista.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="crm-layout-tip">
            <strong>2. Cambiar orden</strong>
            <p>Pulsa Subir o Bajar y el dashboard se recoloca al instante.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="crm-layout-tip">
            <strong>3. Revisar el lienzo</strong>
            <p>Mientras editas, los bloques se remarcan en azul y los ocultos quedan atenuados.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="crm-layout-grid">
          <section class="crm-layout-column">
            <div class="crm-layout-column-head">
              <h3>Tarjetas KPI</h3>
              <p class="crm-inline-note">Ordena de izquierda a derecha dentro del bloque superior.</p>
            </div>
            <div id="clients-kpi-layout-kpis" class="crm-layout-list"></div>
          </section>

          <section class="crm-layout-column">
            <div class="crm-layout-column-head">
              <h3>Bloques del dashboard</h3>
              <p class="crm-inline-note">Controla el orden vertical de los graficos y comparativas.</p>
            </div>
            <div id="clients-kpi-layout-panels" class="crm-layout-list"></div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>

    <section class="crm-grid crm-promo-kpi-grid" aria-live="polite">
      <article
        class="crm-card crm-kpi crm-kpi-highlight crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="kpis"
        data-widget-id="reservations_total"
        data-customize-label="Reservas registradas"
      >
        <div class="crm-kpi-head">
          <p>Reservas registradas</p>
          <button
            class="crm-kpi-help"
            type="button"
            data-help="Total de filas en crm.client_project_reservations para la promocion seleccionada."
          >
            ?
          </button>
        </div>
        <strong id="promo-kpi-reservations-total">-</strong>
        <small class="crm-kpi-sub">Registros reales importados</small>
      </article>

      <article
        class="crm-card crm-kpi crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="kpis"
        data-widget-id="active_reservations"
        data-customize-label="Reservas activas"
      >
        <div class="crm-kpi-head">
          <p>Reservas activas</p>
          <button
            class="crm-kpi-help"
            type="button"
            data-help="Conteo de reservas en estados activos (preinscrito, reserva enviada, reservado, adhesion pagada, contrato firmado). Excluye canceladas y descartadas."
          >
            ?
          </button>
        </div>
        <strong id="promo-kpi-active-reservations">-</strong>
        <small class="crm-kpi-sub">En curso sobre el total historico</small>
      </article>

      <article
        class="crm-card crm-kpi crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="kpis"
        data-widget-id="clients_total"
        data-customize-label="Clientes unicos"
      >
        <div class="crm-kpi-head">
          <p>Clientes unicos</p>
          <button
            class="crm-kpi-help"
            type="button"
            data-help="Conteo de client_id distintos asociados a la promocion seleccionada."
          >
            ?
          </button>
        </div>
        <strong id="promo-kpi-clients-total">-</strong>
        <small class="crm-kpi-sub">Sin duplicar por reservas repetidas</small>
      </article>

      <article
        class="crm-card crm-kpi crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="kpis"
        data-widget-id="ratio"
        data-customize-label="Reservas por cliente"
      >
        <div class="crm-kpi-head">
          <p>Reservas por cliente</p>
          <button
            class="crm-kpi-help"
            type="button"
            data-help="Formula: reservas_total / clientes_unicos de la promocion."
          >
            ?
          </button>
        </div>
        <strong id="promo-kpi-ratio">-</strong>
        <small class="crm-kpi-sub">Intensidad comercial por cliente</small>
      </article>

      <article
        class="crm-card crm-kpi crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="kpis"
        data-widget-id="ticket"
        data-customize-label="Ticket medio sin IVA"
      >
        <div class="crm-kpi-head">
          <p>Ticket medio sin IVA</p>
          <button
            class="crm-kpi-help"
            type="button"
            data-help="Promedio de price_without_vat en las reservas de la promocion con valor numerico valido."
          >
            ?
          </button>
        </div>
        <strong id="promo-kpi-ticket">-</strong>
        <small class="crm-kpi-sub">Base economica por operacion</small>
      </article>

      <article
        class="crm-card crm-kpi crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="kpis"
        data-widget-id="cycle"
        data-customize-label="Ciclo medio"
      >
        <div class="crm-kpi-head">
          <p>Ciclo medio (dias)</p>
          <button
            class="crm-kpi-help"
            type="button"
            data-help="Promedio de transaction_cycle_days en reservas con valor conocido para la promocion."
          >
            ?
          </button>
        </div>
        <strong id="promo-kpi-cycle">-</strong>
        <small class="crm-kpi-sub">Velocidad de cierre</small>
      </article>

      <article
        class="crm-card crm-kpi crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="kpis"
        data-widget-id="reservation_paid"
        data-customize-label="Reserva pagada"
      >
        <div class="crm-kpi-head">
          <p>Reserva pagada</p>
          <button
            class="crm-kpi-help"
            type="button"
            data-help="Porcentaje: is_reservation_paid = true sobre reservas con is_reservation_paid informado."
          >
            ?
          </button>
        </div>
        <strong id="promo-kpi-reservation-paid">-</strong>
        <small class="crm-kpi-sub">Madurez de pago inicial</small>
      </article>

      <article
        class="crm-card crm-kpi crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="kpis"
        data-widget-id="adhesion_paid"
        data-customize-label="Adhesion pagada"
      >
        <div class="crm-kpi-head">
          <p>Adhesion pagada</p>
          <button
            class="crm-kpi-help"
            type="button"
            data-help="Porcentaje: is_adhesion_paid = true sobre reservas con is_adhesion_paid informado."
          >
            ?
          </button>
        </div>
        <strong id="promo-kpi-adhesion-paid">-</strong>
        <small class="crm-kpi-sub">Avance contractual</small>
      </article>

      <article
        class="crm-card crm-kpi crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="kpis"
        data-widget-id="docs"
        data-customize-label="Documentacion completa"
      >
        <div class="crm-kpi-head">
          <p>Documentacion completa</p>
          <button
            class="crm-kpi-help"
            type="button"
            data-help="Porcentaje de checks documentales marcados como true (DNI/Pasaporte, AML y subida) sobre los campos informados."
          >
            ?
          </button>
        </div>
        <strong id="promo-kpi-docs">-</strong>
        <small class="crm-kpi-sub">Cumplimiento documental</small>
      </article>

      <article
        class="crm-card crm-kpi crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="kpis"
        data-widget-id="direct"
        data-customize-label="Canal directo"
      >
        <div class="crm-kpi-head">
          <p>Canal directo</p>
          <button
            class="crm-kpi-help"
            type="button"
            data-help="Porcentaje de reservas con is_direct_sale=true y is_agency_sale!=true sobre total de reservas de la promocion."
          >
            ?
          </button>
        </div>
        <strong id="promo-kpi-direct">-</strong>
        <small class="crm-kpi-sub">Peso de venta directa</small>
      </article>

      <article
        class="crm-card crm-kpi crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="kpis"
        data-widget-id="top_status"
        data-customize-label="Estado lider"
      >
        <div class="crm-kpi-head">
          <p>Estado lider</p>
          <button
            class="crm-kpi-help"
            type="button"
            data-help="Estado con mayor numero de reservas en la promocion segun reservation_status."
          >
            ?
          </button>
        </div>
        <strong id="promo-kpi-top-status">-</strong>
        <small class="crm-kpi-sub">Punto dominante del embudo</small>
      </article>
    </section>

    <div id="clients-kpi-layout-stack" class="crm-dashboard-layout-stack">
      <section
        class="crm-grid crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="panels"
        data-widget-id="overview"
        data-customize-label="Canal comercial y estados"
      >
        <article class="crm-card crm-half">
          <h3>Canal comercial de la promocion</h3>
          <p class="crm-inline-note">
            Distribucion de reservas por canal de venta para la promocion seleccionada.
          </p>
          <div class="crm-channel-layout">
            <div class="crm-chart-wrap">
              <div id="clients-kpi-channel-donut" class="crm-chart-surface crm-chart-surface-compact">
                <p class="crm-inline-note">Cargando grafico de canales...</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <ul id="clients-kpi-channel-legend" class="crm-metric-list">
              <li>Sin datos</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="crm-card crm-half">
          <h3>Estado de reservas en la promocion</h3>
          <p class="crm-inline-note">Ranking de estados para medir avance comercial de la promocion.</p>
          <div id="clients-kpi-status-bars" class="crm-chart-surface">
            <p class="crm-inline-note">Sin datos de estado.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section
        class="crm-card crm-full crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="panels"
        data-widget-id="monthly"
        data-customize-label="Evolucion mensual"
      >
        <h3>Evolucion mensual de la promocion</h3>
        <p class="crm-inline-note">
          Conteo mensual segun reservation_date o fechas de pago registradas.
        </p>
        <div id="clients-kpi-monthly" class="crm-chart-surface crm-chart-surface-wide">
          <p class="crm-inline-note">Sin datos mensuales.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section
        class="crm-card crm-full crm-compare-card crm-dashboard-widget"
        data-dashboard-section="panels"
        data-widget-id="compare"
        data-customize-label="Comparativa entre promociones"
      >
        <div class="crm-compare-headline">
          <div>
            <h2>Comparativa entre promociones</h2>
            <p class="crm-inline-note">
              Ranking para detectar que promociones concentran mayor actividad y calidad de cierre.
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="crm-compare-hint">Pulsa en una barra o en un resumen para abrir su KPI.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="clients-kpi-compare-summary" class="crm-compare-summary">
          <p class="crm-inline-note">Calculando resumen de promociones...</p>
        </div>
        <div class="crm-compare-chart-wrap">
          <div id="clients-kpi-compare" class="crm-chart-surface crm-chart-surface-wide">
            <p class="crm-inline-note">Sin datos de promociones.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="crm-table-wrap crm-compare-table-wrap">
          <table class="crm-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Promocion</th>
                <th>Reservas</th>
                <th>Activas</th>
                <th>% activa</th>
                <th>Clientes</th>
                <th>Res/cliente</th>
                <th>Directo</th>
                <th>Reserva pagada</th>
                <th>Adhesion pagada</th>
                <th>Docs OK</th>
                <th>Ticket</th>
                <th>Ciclo</th>
                <th>Estado lider</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody id="clients-kpi-promotions-tbody">
              <tr>
                <td colspan="13">Cargando dashboard...</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <section class="crm-card crm-full">
      <p id="clients-kpi-feedback" class="crm-feedback">Dashboard listo.</p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .crm-clients-dashboard .crm-form.crm-form-compact {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr));
      align-items: end;
    }

    .crm-dashboard-toolbar {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 0.95rem 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #d4e0ef;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f6faff 0%, #eef5ff 100%);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .crm-dashboard-toolbar-copy {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.18rem;
    }

    .crm-dashboard-toolbar-copy strong {
      color: var(--crm-primary);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .crm-dashboard-toolbar-copy p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #56708d;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      max-width: 58rem;
    }

    .crm-dashboard-toolbar-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .crm-dashboard-toolbar-actions .crm-button {
      min-width: 168px;
      justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 22px -22px rgba(15, 42, 72, 0.86);
    }

    .crm-layout-panel {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #ccd9ea;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 34px -28px rgba(15, 42, 72, 0.6);
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .crm-layout-panel-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .crm-layout-panel-head h3 {
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .crm-layout-presets {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0.85rem 0.95rem;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: #f7faff;
      border: 1px solid #dbe6f4;
    }

    .crm-layout-presets strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--crm-primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.12rem;
    }

    .crm-layout-presets-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .crm-layout-preset-button,
    .crm-layout-action-button {
      border: 1px solid #c8d6e8;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--crm-primary);
      font: inherit;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 0.48rem 0.8rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border-color 0.16s ease, transform 0.16s ease, box-shadow 0.16s ease,
        background-color 0.16s ease;
    }

    .crm-layout-preset-button:hover,
    .crm-layout-action-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      border-color: #91a9c8;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 20px -22px rgba(15, 42, 72, 0.92);
    }

    .crm-layout-action-button[disabled] {
      opacity: 0.42;
      cursor: not-allowed;
      transform: none;
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    .crm-layout-action-button.is-toggle {
      background: #edf4ff;
      border-color: #b6c8e0;
    }

    .crm-layout-guide {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .crm-layout-tip {
      padding: 0.85rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid #dde6f2;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fdfefe 0%, #f7fbff 100%);
    }

    .crm-layout-tip strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
      color: var(--crm-primary);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }

    .crm-layout-tip p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #5c738d;
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .crm-layout-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(320px, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .crm-layout-column {
      min-width: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .crm-layout-column-head h3 {
      margin-bottom: 0.16rem;
    }

    .crm-layout-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.55rem;
    }

    .crm-layout-row {
      padding: 0.78rem 0.85rem;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid #d5e0ee;
      background: #f8fbff;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .crm-layout-row.is-hidden {
      background: #fff8ef;
      border-color: #f0d2a1;
    }

    .crm-layout-row-copy {
      min-width: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.18rem;
    }

    .crm-layout-row-copy strong {
      color: var(--crm-primary);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      line-height: 1.28;
    }

    .crm-layout-row-copy small {
      color: #61768e;
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .crm-layout-row-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.45rem;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .crm-layout-status {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.32rem 0.62rem;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: #315274;
      background: #eaf2ff;
      border: 1px solid #c9daf1;
    }

    .crm-layout-row.is-hidden .crm-layout-status {
      color: #8a5a16;
      background: #fff0d7;
      border-color: #f0cf96;
    }

    .crm-dashboard-layout-stack {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .crm-toggle-label {
      min-height: 2.55rem;
      align-content: center;
      border: 1px solid #cfd8e8;
      border-radius: 11px;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.58rem;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .crm-toggle-label span {
